{"tid":97182,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇我親戚讀緊thei，想重考dse?","createTime":"2017-01-27T12:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T13:19:04.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5848b39922dbf4a84d9eda951a84e7f47e229a1a","tid":97182,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"佢讀咗一個月都冇就開始走堂<br />\n好似係個科唔啱佢<br />\n之後佢話想重考dse<br />\n但係佢低我幾分<br />\n（唔sure幾分，我就垃圾得19分）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我見佢呢啲玩心咁重<br />\n又有女（讀緊shitty），真係唔睇好佢囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最衰佢係文科仔<br />\n唔係嘅話中大工程應該幫到佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭先仲聽到我親戚開玩笑咁串佢話：兩兄弟一齊考咪鬥低分囉<br />\n我心諗可能係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25050de7060adc61d533c60e8f1f8f41e4593e22","tid":97182,"uid":37415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abdc4cac9c8084203735060fb6a7a5dcb0a8fd53","tid":97182,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔多鍾意佢<br />\n原因太長廢事打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考之前又串又盛<br />\n未放榜個時又講到夠入medic咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢出到嚟呢個成績<br />\n唔笑佢真係好難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我葡萄佢<br />\n屋企有錢，不停補習<br />\n又買一堆參考書<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢啲嘢認真唔係必要，<br />\n有唔代表成績好<br />\n冇唔代表成績差<br />\n<br />\n但望佢真係有少少葡萄...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩五十步笑百步吖<br />\n根本我兩個都咁垃圾"},{"pid":"95b4da18178725d222eb3f2799673add25861aa3","tid":97182,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0